name: Supporter Token (April 2022)
description:
You can choose to support Untrusted for April 2022, because you are amazing!

As a gift, you also will get an exclusive badge, the Murderous Fool avatar and 16384 in-game credits.
Thank you so much!

You must purchase this from the in-game store, or open the in-game store after purchase to apply this item to your steam-linked account.
